title: Lala Interview and more
itunes:title: Lala Interview and more
description:
Today on the show we had friend to the show Lala call in where she spoke how she is holding up during the quarantine as well with her new show about herself and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Ellen because of her comments comparing her quarantine lifestyle to jail and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"
